author: @ValentinaGoti
text:
Hi blackpink! My name is Viola, I'm 12 years old, I come from Italy and I'm a huge fan of yours.
I miss you so much please come back. My biggest dream is to go to one of your concerts and see you live. I know it might not seem like much to you, but I can assure you that it really matters to me, more than you think.
After Born Pink, which I wasn't able to go to, I hoped with all my heart that one day you would do another concert, but that day never came.
One day I saw a video of your dishband. After that news I burst into tears, at that moment I could no longer perceive emotions, I was completely shocked, how would I have lived without blackpink? Of course, we always have your songs, but it's not the same, we will no longer have the serenity of knowing that you are still united. Believe me, it hurts more than a stab wound. Sometimes I think, "maybe they just need a break, or it's over for them forever" and I start to cry.
I love you so much blackpink. I will never forget you.😢🖤💗
